1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:01,500
<i> Four locations,</i>

2
00:00:01,500 --> 00:00:02,700
<i>but all of them are outside
the hotel.</i>

3
00:00:03,667 --> 00:00:05,300
<i> The point of intersection.</i>

4
00:00:05,300 --> 00:00:07,033
<i> It's on Hotel 88's property.</i>

5
00:00:07,033 --> 00:00:08,767
<i> The treasure is here.</i>

6
00:00:08,767 --> 00:00:10,233
<i> Over there, under the tree.</i>

7
00:00:11,067 --> 00:00:12,167
[BODY THUDS]

8
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:14,600
<i> Dad!</i>

9
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:17,200
<i> Dad, Dad, Dad, Dad!</i>

10
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:18,133
<i> Dad...</i>

11
00:00:18,567 --> 00:00:20,533
<i> Wake up, Dad! Wake up!</i>

12
00:00:22,367 --> 00:00:24,067
He used to be Dad's contractor.

13
00:00:24,067 --> 00:00:25,667
<i>So he knows the ins and outs
of this hotel.</i>

14
00:00:25,667 --> 00:00:28,033
<i>He might know about
the hidden basement.</i>

15
00:00:28,033 --> 00:00:29,000
<i> This is it.</i>

16
00:00:30,633 --> 00:00:32,100
<i> I'll go in.</i>

17
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:34,667
<i> Come back alive, okay?</i>

18
00:00:37,133 --> 00:00:38,233
<i> Gio?</i>

19
00:00:38,233 --> 00:00:40,100
<i>- Gio!
- Gio!</i>

20
00:00:40,100 --> 00:00:42,333
<i>Gio, there's a bomb!
There's a bomb!</i>

21
00:00:42,333 --> 00:00:44,467
<i>- Gio, there's a bomb!
- There's a bomb!</i>

22
00:00:44,467 --> 00:00:45,767
<i> Help us.</i>

23
00:00:45,767 --> 00:00:48,200
[CHESKA AND TRIXIE CRYING]

24
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:51,033
- We're not going to make it!
- We're not going to make it!

25
00:00:51,033 --> 00:00:54,167
- [TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]
- [TRIXIE AND CHESKA CRYING]

26
00:00:54,167 --> 00:00:55,167
Gio...

27
00:00:55,567 --> 00:00:57,267
[BOMB BEEPING]

28
00:00:57,267 --> 00:00:59,700
- Gio...
- We're not going to make it!

29
00:00:59,700 --> 00:01:01,467
- [GIO GROANS]
- [CHAINS RATTLING]

30
00:01:01,467 --> 00:01:03,433
- [TRIXIE CRYING]
- We won't make it.

31
00:01:03,433 --> 00:01:04,633
Let's pull it up. Come on.

32
00:01:04,633 --> 00:01:07,033
- Carry it?
- Yeah, let's pull it up.

33
00:01:07,033 --> 00:01:09,333
Somebody help us!

34
00:01:09,367 --> 00:01:10,700
[CRYING, COUGHING]

35
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:12,467
- Help us...
- One, two...

36
00:01:12,467 --> 00:01:15,200
[GRUNTING]

37
00:01:16,567 --> 00:01:18,200
One more time.

38
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,700
One, two...

39
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:21,800
[GRUNTING]

40
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:28,367
[OBJECTS SCATTERING]

41
00:01:28,367 --> 00:01:31,800
Gio, just go! [SOBS]

42
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:34,133
- We're not going to make it!
- We will.

43
00:01:34,133 --> 00:01:36,100
- [CLANKING]
- [TRIXIE CRYING]

44
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,500
[CHESKA]
We're not going to make it!

45
00:01:37,500 --> 00:01:40,567
[GRUNTING]

46
00:01:41,433 --> 00:01:43,100
Gio, just leave us.

47
00:01:44,133 --> 00:01:45,433
[GRUNTING]

48
00:01:45,433 --> 00:01:47,667
[CHESKA] Think of your siblings!

49
00:01:47,667 --> 00:01:49,533
- Gio, please...
- [GRUNTING]

50
00:01:49,533 --> 00:01:52,333
Save yourself!

51
00:01:52,333 --> 00:01:54,267
We can't all die here!

52
00:01:54,267 --> 00:01:55,867
One of us should live!

53
00:01:55,867 --> 00:01:57,100
[CRYING]

54
00:01:57,100 --> 00:01:59,167
- [TRIXIE] Gio, please!
- [CHESKA] Just go!

55
00:01:59,167 --> 00:02:03,500
- [TRIXIE] Save yourself!
- Please just go!

56
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:05,600
[CHESKA] I'll leave Kiko to you.

57
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:08,433
- [CHESKA] Look after him.
- [TRIXIE] Gio, please! Just go!

58
00:02:08,433 --> 00:02:09,433
[GASPS]

59
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:11,867
[GASPS]

60
00:02:11,867 --> 00:02:14,367
[WHIMPERS] Thank you.

61
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,400
Cheska!

62
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,267
[CRYING]

63
00:02:17,267 --> 00:02:19,200
[CHESKA] Hang in there!

64
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:21,700
[CLANKING]

65
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:24,733
[GIO GRUNTING]

66
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,733
[CLANKING]

67
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:30,467
Come on, Trixie!

68
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,333
Ouch! [WHIMPERS]

69
00:02:34,233 --> 00:02:35,800
[BOMB BEEPING]

70
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:42,400
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

71
00:02:43,367 --> 00:02:45,300
- [EXPLOSION]
- [SCREAMING]

72
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:47,533
[EXPLOSION]

73
00:02:49,733 --> 00:02:51,267
- [EXPLOSION]
- [SCREAMING]

74
00:02:51,267 --> 00:02:52,500
[PANICKED BREATHING]

75
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:53,567
Trixie?

76
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:55,500
Cheska?

77
00:02:55,500 --> 00:02:57,433
Gio? Gio! I need to--

78
00:02:57,433 --> 00:03:00,567
- Luna, don't!
- We need to save Gio!

79
00:03:00,567 --> 00:03:03,367
Let me go, Justin!
I need to save him!

80
00:03:03,367 --> 00:03:04,733
Luna, stop! It's dangerous!

81
00:03:04,733 --> 00:03:06,933
[WAILING] Gio!

82
00:03:06,933 --> 00:03:09,700
- Gio!
- Come on! Let's go!

83
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:10,767
Gio!

84
00:03:10,767 --> 00:03:17,700
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

85
00:04:10,433 --> 00:04:12,933
- [EXPLOSION]
- [SCREAMING, GRUNTING]

86
00:04:12,933 --> 00:04:16,333
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

87
00:04:16,333 --> 00:04:18,567
[GRUNTING, COUGHING]

88
00:04:18,567 --> 00:04:19,633
Luna, stop! It's dangerous!

89
00:04:19,633 --> 00:04:22,933
- We need to save Gio!
- Luna, stop it! Stop it!

90
00:04:22,933 --> 00:04:24,367
Let me go!

91
00:04:24,367 --> 00:04:25,867
- Gio!
- No!

92
00:04:25,867 --> 00:04:28,233
- Gio! [SOBBING]
- You can't!

93
00:04:28,267 --> 00:04:29,300
Luna!

94
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:31,867
Let go of me!

95
00:04:31,867 --> 00:04:36,933
- [SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]
- [CHESKA AND TRIXIE COUGHING]

96
00:04:36,933 --> 00:04:37,933
Cheska?

97
00:04:37,933 --> 00:04:39,933
[CHESKA AND TRIXIE COUGHING]

98
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:41,367
Trixie?

99
00:04:41,733 --> 00:04:45,867
[CHESKA AND TRIXIE COUGHING]

100
00:04:45,867 --> 00:04:47,900
[LUNA] How about Gio?

101
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:49,300
Where's Gio?

102
00:04:50,633 --> 00:04:53,500
- [GIO COUGHING]
- [CHESKA AND TRIXIE SOBBING]

103
00:04:56,833 --> 00:04:57,900
Gio!

104
00:04:57,900 --> 00:05:04,733
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

105
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,067
[LUNA SOBS]

106
00:05:08,067 --> 00:05:09,567
I thought...

107
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,733
I thought you weren't
coming back to me.

108
00:05:14,367 --> 00:05:15,367
[GIO SNIFFLES]

109
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:18,333
I told you, remember?

110
00:05:19,467 --> 00:05:22,633
No matter what happens,
I won't leave you.

111
00:05:25,067 --> 00:05:28,567
[GIO SOBS]

112
00:05:28,567 --> 00:05:35,533
[DRAMATIC MUSIC CONTINUES]

113
00:05:37,033 --> 00:05:39,667
- [SOBBING]
- [SMOOCHING]

114
00:05:39,667 --> 00:05:43,700
[COUGHING, SOBBING]

115
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:44,867
Oh my god!

116
00:05:46,333 --> 00:05:48,767
I thought we wouldn't
make it, Justin.

117
00:05:48,767 --> 00:05:51,400
We really thought
we'd die there.

118
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:52,400
- Where's Martin?
- Where's Kiko?

119
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,367
Don't worry about them.

120
00:05:54,367 --> 00:05:55,433
I'm glad you're safe.

121
00:05:55,433 --> 00:06:01,700
[SOBBING]

122
00:06:05,967 --> 00:06:07,033
[TRIXIE] Oh my god...

123
00:06:12,433 --> 00:06:13,667
How are you guys?

124
00:06:13,667 --> 00:06:14,867
Are you hurt anywhere?

125
00:06:15,467 --> 00:06:16,733
Uh...

126
00:06:16,733 --> 00:06:18,800
I just got some scrapes.

127
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:21,500
How about you, Trixie?

128
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:23,500
I'm fine.

129
00:06:24,633 --> 00:06:26,367
Come on, let's get out of here.

130
00:06:26,367 --> 00:06:28,733
Justin, go back to the hotel.

131
00:06:28,733 --> 00:06:30,133
I'll take care of them.

132
00:06:30,133 --> 00:06:32,400
[LUNA] What about you?
Where are you going?

133
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:36,100
I'm going to follow Kiko
and the others.

134
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:38,367
- [CHESKA] What happened to him?
- I'll take care of it.

135
00:06:38,367 --> 00:06:40,600
Gio, get checked
at the hospital first.

136
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:43,100
We don't have time, Luna.
I'll be back.

137
00:06:43,667 --> 00:06:44,967
- I'll be back.
- Gio.

138
00:06:44,967 --> 00:06:46,100
- Gio.
- Go.

139
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:47,333
- Be careful.
- Go now.

140
00:06:47,333 --> 00:06:49,467
- Gio, what about Kiko?
- Come on, let's go.

141
00:06:49,467 --> 00:06:51,700
- What happened to--
- Let's go. Luna, come on.

142
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:53,867
[CHESKA SOBBING]

143
00:06:53,867 --> 00:06:55,967
[JADE] We've been here
since forever.

144
00:06:55,967 --> 00:06:57,800
Aren't we supposed
to see it now

145
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:00,367
or at least a hint
that we're getting close?

146
00:07:05,967 --> 00:07:06,967
What is this?

147
00:07:08,567 --> 00:07:09,733
What's that?

148
00:07:09,733 --> 00:07:10,700
Why?

149
00:07:11,833 --> 00:07:12,833
It's not a rock.

150
00:07:13,467 --> 00:07:14,400
What?

151
00:07:18,767 --> 00:07:20,133
[MARTIN] It's a rock?!

152
00:07:20,533 --> 00:07:21,400
[SCREAMS]

153
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,067
Come on, guys.

154
00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:26,867
This is not the time
to give up!

155
00:07:26,867 --> 00:07:28,800
This is for Trixie and
for Cheska,

156
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,133
for your sisters!

157
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:33,167
Come on, let's keep going!
Hurry up!

158
00:07:34,867 --> 00:07:36,033
Martin!

159
00:07:36,033 --> 00:07:36,933
Kiko!

160
00:07:38,167 --> 00:07:39,400
Come on!

161
00:07:41,167 --> 00:07:43,067
[GRUNTS]

162
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,033
[GRUNTS]

163
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:54,033
[JADE PANTING]

164
00:07:54,667 --> 00:08:01,633
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

165
00:08:01,633 --> 00:08:02,700
[GRUNTS]

166
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,900
[GRUNTS, BREATHES HEAVILY]

167
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,933
Dad...

168
00:08:22,267 --> 00:08:23,267
Dad.

169
00:08:23,267 --> 00:08:24,800
[BREATHES SHAKILY]

170
00:08:27,900 --> 00:08:29,000
[THUDS]

171
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:34,933
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

172
00:08:37,067 --> 00:08:41,500
[LEAVES RUSTLING]

173
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:51,567
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

174
00:09:11,067 --> 00:09:17,900
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

175
00:09:25,833 --> 00:09:27,867
He was looking
for something from us.

176
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,667
A map.

177
00:09:35,967 --> 00:09:37,700
I didn't really understand it.

178
00:09:38,167 --> 00:09:40,267
Then all of a sudden,
he attacked Dad.

179
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,500
I passed out too.

180
00:09:48,633 --> 00:09:49,933
When I woke up...

181
00:09:55,233 --> 00:09:56,533
...he was already gone.

182
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:00,133
Do you know who did this?

183
00:10:02,267 --> 00:10:03,633
Sandro.

184
00:10:03,633 --> 00:10:07,800
- [TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]
- [CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING]

185
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,733
That's what Dad called him.

186
00:10:11,300 --> 00:10:12,633
What does he look like?

187
00:10:13,667 --> 00:10:14,900
He has long hair.

188
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:19,000
His eyes are terrifying.

189
00:10:22,567 --> 00:10:23,633
Positive.

190
00:10:24,033 --> 00:10:25,267
Radio this to Syvera.

191
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,200
This is the Sandro
they're looking for.

192
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:31,100
- [TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING]

193
00:10:31,100 --> 00:10:32,200
[EDWARD] What do you mean?

194
00:10:32,833 --> 00:10:34,233
The Sandro you're describing

195
00:10:34,867 --> 00:10:37,067
is the same Sandro the people
at Hotel 88 are after.

196
00:10:37,967 --> 00:10:39,767
Aren't they your friends?

197
00:10:39,767 --> 00:10:46,800
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

198
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:47,767
[SNIFFLES]

199
00:10:48,867 --> 00:10:50,167
[GEORGIA] Cheska?!

200
00:10:50,167 --> 00:10:51,700
[SOBS] Ma!

201
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:56,067
[CRYING, SOBBING]

202
00:10:56,067 --> 00:10:57,800
Ma... [SOBS]

203
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:59,267
[GEORGIA] Cheska, my dear!

204
00:10:59,267 --> 00:11:05,367
[CRYING, SOBBING]

205
00:11:05,367 --> 00:11:06,667
I'm sorry, Ma.

206
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:10,933
[CRYING, SOBBING]

207
00:11:10,967 --> 00:11:13,933
I thought I'd never
see you again.

208
00:11:13,933 --> 00:11:17,067
[CRYING, SOBBING]

209
00:11:17,067 --> 00:11:18,967
Kiko? Where's Kiko?

210
00:11:18,967 --> 00:11:20,800
[SOBBING]

211
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:22,800
He's on his way back.
He's coming back here.

212
00:11:23,767 --> 00:11:24,933
What about Martin?

213
00:11:24,933 --> 00:11:26,033
[CRIES]

214
00:11:26,033 --> 00:11:27,733
Where's Martin?

215
00:11:28,067 --> 00:11:29,333
[SOBBING]

216
00:11:29,333 --> 00:11:31,767
He's coming back with Kiko.

217
00:11:33,033 --> 00:11:34,400
Are you okay?

218
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:36,033
[BREATH QUIVERS]
Huh?

219
00:11:36,033 --> 00:11:38,633
My goodness, you kids.

220
00:11:38,633 --> 00:11:41,333
What on earth
has been happening?

221
00:11:42,033 --> 00:11:44,200
[SOBBING, SNIFFLING]

222
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:46,900
- [DIGGING]
- [GRUNTING]

223
00:11:49,367 --> 00:11:50,800
Martin.

224
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:53,767
[KIKO] I think this is
the door to the treasure.

225
00:11:54,833 --> 00:11:58,867
[SCRAPING SOIL]

226
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:04,433
[CHUCKLING SOFTLY]

227
00:12:04,433 --> 00:12:05,400
Kiko...

228
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:08,100
[LAUGHING]

229
00:12:08,100 --> 00:12:09,967
[GIO] Kiko! Martin!

230
00:12:09,967 --> 00:12:11,333
- [KIKO] Gio!
- [JADE] Gio!

231
00:12:11,333 --> 00:12:12,633
[JADE] Gio!

232
00:12:12,633 --> 00:12:14,267
- What happened to you?
- [JADE] What happened?

233
00:12:14,300 --> 00:12:16,133
Cheska and Trixie
are safe now.

234
00:12:16,133 --> 00:12:17,233
- [EXHALES DEEPLY]
- Really?!

235
00:12:17,233 --> 00:12:18,233
[PANTING]

236
00:12:18,233 --> 00:12:20,433
[MARTIN] They're back?
Sandro let them go?

237
00:12:21,067 --> 00:12:22,833
No. I found them.

238
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,867
In the hotel's hidden basement.

239
00:12:25,367 --> 00:12:27,833
They're on their way back
with Luna and Justin.

240
00:12:28,367 --> 00:12:29,867
- Thank God.
- Thank you.

241
00:12:29,867 --> 00:12:30,933
Thank you, bro!

242
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,767
Thank you!

243
00:12:32,767 --> 00:12:33,967
Thank you for saving
my sister.

244
00:12:33,967 --> 00:12:35,367
Alright, no worries.

245
00:12:35,367 --> 00:12:36,767
We need to get out of here.

246
00:12:36,767 --> 00:12:37,767
Kiko!

247
00:12:38,133 --> 00:12:39,800
- [JADE] Edward?!
- It's Sandro!

248
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:42,167
Edward?!
What happened to you?

249
00:12:42,167 --> 00:12:43,200
[EDWARD]
They're looking for you.

250
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,200
They won't stop until--

251
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,300
[SANDRO SCREAMS]

252
00:12:45,300 --> 00:12:46,133
[GUNSHOTS]

253
00:12:46,133 --> 00:12:48,267
- Jade, get down!
- [JADE WHIMPERS]

254
00:12:48,933 --> 00:12:50,400
[GUNSHOTS]

255
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:52,200
- [SCREAMS]
- [JADE] Martin! Martin!

256
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,433
Sandro's never going
to stop coming after us!

257
00:12:53,433 --> 00:12:54,800
Kiko, protect Jade!

258
00:12:56,167 --> 00:12:59,867
[PANTING]

259
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,433
Kiko, go home with Jade.

260
00:13:03,433 --> 00:13:04,767
Edward, go with them!

261
00:13:04,767 --> 00:13:06,833
Gio, we're not
leaving you here!

262
00:13:06,833 --> 00:13:08,367
Jade, you need to get home
to your siblings!

263
00:13:08,367 --> 00:13:10,067
- Kiko!
- It's just the two of us now.

264
00:13:10,767 --> 00:13:11,767
One...

265
00:13:11,767 --> 00:13:14,333
[SANDRO PANTING]

266
00:13:14,333 --> 00:13:15,800
- Two! Three!
- Two! Three!

267
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:17,200
- Run!
- Go, go, go!

268
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:20,367
[GASPING]

269
00:13:20,367 --> 00:13:21,767
[MARTIN] Gio, hurry!

270
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:23,467
- He might catch us, Gio!
- Wait!

271
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,800
[SCREAMING]

272
00:13:29,767 --> 00:13:31,900
- [MARTIN] Hurry up, Gio!
- [SANDRO SCREAMING]

273
00:13:31,900 --> 00:13:33,233
[SCREAMS]

274
00:13:33,233 --> 00:13:40,200
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

275
00:13:41,333 --> 00:13:43,033
- [JADE] Hurry! Hurry!
- [KIKO] Hurry up!

276
00:13:43,033 --> 00:13:44,967
- [JADE] Hurry!
- [EDWARD] Let's hide!

277
00:13:44,967 --> 00:13:46,467
- [PANTING]
- Careful! Careful!

278
00:13:49,367 --> 00:13:51,067
- [SANDRO SCREAMING]
- [PANTING]

279
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:54,800
[SCREAMS]

280
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:55,800
[GIO] Martin!

281
00:13:57,133 --> 00:13:58,400
- [GUNSHOT]
- [THUD]

282
00:13:58,400 --> 00:14:05,333
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

283
00:14:07,467 --> 00:14:09,000
We can't leave them behind!

284
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,867
Please, we have to go back!

285
00:14:11,167 --> 00:14:13,200
- Edward, Kiko, hurry up!
- Let's go!

286
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:16,933
- [BLOWS LANDING]
- [THUDS]

287
00:14:18,367 --> 00:14:19,833
- [THWACKS]
- Aah!

288
00:14:19,833 --> 00:14:23,967
[HIGH-PITCHED RINGING]

289
00:14:23,967 --> 00:14:25,033
- Aah!
- [GUN THUDS]

290
00:14:27,900 --> 00:14:32,300
- [THWACKING]
- [GRUNTING]

291
00:14:32,333 --> 00:14:33,300
[KICK LANDS]

292
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:34,867
[GRUNTING]

293
00:14:34,867 --> 00:14:36,133
- [BLOWS LANDING]
- [THWACKS]

294
00:14:36,133 --> 00:14:38,600
[GRUNTING]

295
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,567
[THUDS]

296
00:14:39,567 --> 00:14:44,300
[GRUNTING]

297
00:14:46,333 --> 00:14:47,433
[BLOW LANDS]

298
00:14:49,033 --> 00:14:50,900
[BLOWS LANDING]

299
00:14:52,467 --> 00:14:54,200
- Aah!
- [THWACKS]

300
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:58,433
- [THWACKING]
- [GRUNTING]

301
00:14:58,433 --> 00:14:59,900
- [KICK LANDS]
- [JADE GRUNTS]

302
00:15:00,467 --> 00:15:01,567
[BLOW LANDS]

303
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:03,333
- [GRUNTING]
- [KICK LANDS]

304
00:15:04,567 --> 00:15:06,233
[JADE BREATHES HEAVILY]

305
00:15:06,233 --> 00:15:10,333
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

306
00:15:10,333 --> 00:15:11,300
[GUN CLICKS]

307
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:13,267
- [WHIMPERS]
- [GUN CLICKS]

308
00:15:13,267 --> 00:15:14,600
Aah! Aah!

309
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:19,100
[BOTH SCREAMING]

310
00:15:19,100 --> 00:15:26,067
[JADE WAILING, BREATHES HEAVILY]

311
00:15:27,867 --> 00:15:29,433
Tell me where the treasure is...

312
00:15:30,433 --> 00:15:32,200
or I'll kill this woman!

313
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,267
[CRIES]

314
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,000
Jade!

315
00:15:37,133 --> 00:15:39,233
[CRYING]

316
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,233
[CRYING, SOBBING]

317
00:15:46,067 --> 00:15:47,533
We'll show you.

318
00:15:47,533 --> 00:15:49,033
[JADE BREATHES HEAVILY]

319
00:15:49,033 --> 00:15:50,567
Just let Jade go.

320
00:15:51,233 --> 00:15:54,167
- [SOBS, SCREAMS]
- Don't fool me!

321
00:15:55,133 --> 00:15:56,167
Don't!

322
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,200
Gio...

323
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:02,267
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

324
00:16:02,267 --> 00:16:06,600
[CRYING, SOBBING]

325
00:16:10,733 --> 00:16:12,600
[JADE SOBBING]

326
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:14,233
[SANDRO] Hurry up!

327
00:16:15,900 --> 00:16:17,767
- [CRYING, SOBBING]
- [EDWARD] Stay still.

328
00:16:17,767 --> 00:16:18,867
Don't touch Jade.

329
00:16:18,867 --> 00:16:22,800
[CRYING, SOBBING]

330
00:16:22,800 --> 00:16:25,833
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

331
00:16:25,833 --> 00:16:27,667
[JADE WAILS] Ouch!

332
00:16:27,667 --> 00:16:29,733
- Don't hurt Jade.
- Ouch!

333
00:16:29,733 --> 00:16:32,133
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

334
00:16:32,133 --> 00:16:33,133
[JADE GRUNTS]

335
00:16:34,167 --> 00:16:40,833
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

336
00:16:40,833 --> 00:16:42,633
[GIO] Here! This is it!

337
00:16:42,667 --> 00:16:44,633
It's yours!
The treasure is yours!

338
00:16:44,633 --> 00:16:46,767
- [JADE] Ouch!
- Just let Jade go!

339
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:50,933
[GIO] Let her go now, Sandro!

340
00:16:52,233 --> 00:16:54,133
- I'm not stupid.
- [JADE SOBS]

341
00:16:54,133 --> 00:16:55,600
I'll take out everyone

342
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:57,633
who stands in the way
of my treasure first!

343
00:16:58,067 --> 00:16:59,667
Jade, stay right there.

344
00:16:59,667 --> 00:17:01,800
You're no longer useful to me!

345
00:17:02,167 --> 00:17:03,933
So you all need
to disappear too!

346
00:17:05,100 --> 00:17:07,967
Just like what I did
to your fathers!

347
00:17:07,967 --> 00:17:13,633
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

348
00:17:13,633 --> 00:17:15,067
[GIO] You're unbelievable,
Sandro.

349
00:17:15,967 --> 00:17:17,367
You're such a monster, Sandro.

350
00:17:24,733 --> 00:17:26,300
You killed our fathers!

351
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:27,767
Gio, please!

352
00:17:27,767 --> 00:17:29,000
- Gio, please!
- You're a monster!

353
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:31,033
You killed our father!

354
00:17:31,633 --> 00:17:32,767
Gio, please!

355
00:17:32,767 --> 00:17:34,933
[SANDRO] Because they didn't
give me what I needed!

356
00:17:35,967 --> 00:17:37,400
- They're a hindrance!
- [JADE] You...

357
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:40,133
And anyone who gets
in my way gets killed!

358
00:17:40,667 --> 00:17:41,800
You...

359
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:45,300
[SOBS] You killed our fathers.

360
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:49,133
[SOBS] It's you...

361
00:17:49,167 --> 00:17:50,900
- [SOBS] You're a demon!
- [EDWARD] Jade...

362
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:52,067
- Jade!
- Jade!

363
00:17:52,067 --> 00:17:53,967
- You're a demon!
- Jade, please!

364
00:17:53,967 --> 00:17:55,700
You're worse than the devil!

365
00:17:55,700 --> 00:17:58,933
Those were our fathers and
you just killed them like that!

366
00:17:58,933 --> 00:18:00,733
- Jade!
- [JADE] How dare you!

367
00:18:00,733 --> 00:18:02,733
- Jade, please don't!
- Stay there, Jade!

368
00:18:02,733 --> 00:18:04,767
- Jade!
- [JADE] You're heartless!

369
00:18:04,767 --> 00:18:05,767
Jade, no!

370
00:18:05,767 --> 00:18:07,200
Shameless! You're a devil!

371
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:09,133
- You're worse than the devil!
- Jade, please!

372
00:18:09,133 --> 00:18:12,033
[CRYING] How dare you!

373
00:18:12,033 --> 00:18:14,400
I killed your fathers first.

374
00:18:15,167 --> 00:18:18,233
Second is your brother!

375
00:18:18,233 --> 00:18:19,367
[WHIMPERS]

376
00:18:20,433 --> 00:18:23,100
You killed my brother?

377
00:18:23,133 --> 00:18:28,400
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

378
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:31,167
I don't care about them.

379
00:18:34,267 --> 00:18:38,167
What matters to me
is my treasure and my family.

380
00:18:38,167 --> 00:18:39,833
Treasure for my son!

381
00:18:39,833 --> 00:18:41,067
[SOBBING] You're so selfish.

382
00:18:41,067 --> 00:18:42,100
You're unbelievable.

383
00:18:42,100 --> 00:18:44,033
You destroyed our families!

384
00:18:44,033 --> 00:18:45,067
Martin, please.

385
00:18:45,067 --> 00:18:47,000
You made us believe
they killed each other!

386
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:49,700
Because I'd do anything
for treasure!

387
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:50,767
[CRIES]

388
00:18:50,767 --> 00:18:52,967
I'll play with your lives!

389
00:18:52,967 --> 00:18:53,900
[WAILS]

390
00:18:53,900 --> 00:18:56,133
- I killed your brother first?
- [WAILS]

391
00:18:56,167 --> 00:18:58,433
- Your brother, huh?!
- [CRYING]

392
00:18:58,433 --> 00:18:59,833
- So be it!
- [GUNSHOT]

393
00:18:59,833 --> 00:19:00,833
- [JADE] Aah! Martin!
- [THUDS]

394
00:19:00,833 --> 00:19:01,833
- Martin!
- Martin!

395
00:19:01,833 --> 00:19:03,333
- Martin!
- Jade!

396
00:19:03,333 --> 00:19:04,500
- Aah!
- [KIKO] Jade!

397
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:05,700
[JADE] Martin!

398
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:08,167
[EDWARD] I beg you, Sandro,
don't hurt Jade!

399
00:19:08,167 --> 00:19:09,800
- Martin!
- Don't hurt Jade!

400
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,067
Don't hurt Jade!

401
00:19:11,067 --> 00:19:13,233
Sandro, I'm begging you.
Don't hurt Jade.

402
00:19:13,233 --> 00:19:14,767
[KIKO] We won't leave you,
Martin, please.

403
00:19:14,767 --> 00:19:18,433
[JADE WAILING]

404
00:19:18,433 --> 00:19:21,100
Martin! Martin!

405
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:22,733
- Martin, hold on!
- Don't hurt Jade!

406
00:19:22,733 --> 00:19:24,867
[LABORED BREATHING]

407
00:19:24,867 --> 00:19:26,267
Martin, please! Hold on!

408
00:19:26,267 --> 00:19:27,233
[CRYING]

409
00:19:27,233 --> 00:19:28,800
We won't leave you!

410
00:19:28,833 --> 00:19:31,067
I won't leave here
if we're incomplete, Martin.

411
00:19:31,067 --> 00:19:35,933
[WAILING]

412
00:19:39,267 --> 00:19:40,700
Let Jade go.

413
00:19:40,833 --> 00:19:44,933
[JADE WAILING] It hurts.

414
00:19:45,067 --> 00:19:48,033
I will give you all of
my father's possessions.

415
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:52,433
Dad owes you a lot, right?

416
00:19:52,567 --> 00:19:55,433
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

417
00:19:55,567 --> 00:19:56,933
I'll give you everything

418
00:19:57,067 --> 00:19:59,400
as payment for all the trouble
he has given you.

419
00:19:59,533 --> 00:20:02,200
Martin!

420
00:20:02,367 --> 00:20:05,767
[EDWARD] You will have all of
the treasure in Hotel 88.

421
00:20:05,900 --> 00:20:08,300
You'll have the wealth
of the Arellanos.

422
00:20:10,633 --> 00:20:12,467
[EDWARD] That's a lot, Sandro.

423
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:13,867
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

424
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:16,267
Let Jade go for me.

425
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:17,500
- [JADE] Edward, Edward...
- [KIKO] Edward...

426
00:20:17,633 --> 00:20:18,767
[JADE] No!

427
00:20:18,900 --> 00:20:20,533
- [KIKO] Edward, Edward!
- [JADE] Don't do this.

428
00:20:20,667 --> 00:20:23,500
You can only get all of
the treasure if I'm with you.

429
00:20:23,633 --> 00:20:26,033
- [KIKO] Edward!
- Believe me, Sandro.

430
00:20:26,167 --> 00:20:28,467
[JADE WAILING]

431
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:30,833
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

432
00:20:30,967 --> 00:20:35,000
[WAILING CONTINUES]

433
00:20:35,167 --> 00:20:36,933
Martin!

434
00:20:37,067 --> 00:20:39,067
You've been blinded
by your greed.

435
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:40,633
[SANDRO] The treasure is mine!

436
00:20:40,767 --> 00:20:43,067
Wealth can be replaced!

437
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:44,433
But a family?

438
00:20:44,567 --> 00:20:45,333
You can't!

439
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:51,233
[LEON GROANS]

440
00:20:51,367 --> 00:20:52,433
<i>- Leon!
- Kiko!</i>

441
00:20:52,567 --> 00:20:53,600
<i> Run!</i>

442
00:20:53,733 --> 00:20:55,367
<i> Kiko! Go!</i>

443
00:20:55,500 --> 00:20:57,967
[LEON] Run away, Kiko! Escape!

444
00:20:58,100 --> 00:21:01,467
<i>I promise I won't waste
Leon's sacrifice for me.</i>

445
00:21:01,600 --> 00:21:07,733
[MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]

446
00:21:07,867 --> 00:21:09,400
[SANDRO] The treasure is mine!

447
00:21:09,567 --> 00:21:11,167
[SOBBING]

448
00:21:11,300 --> 00:21:12,333
Your plans?

449
00:21:12,467 --> 00:21:14,500
Your plans are all nonsense!

450
00:21:14,633 --> 00:21:15,867
- [SANDRO] It's mine!
- No matter what happens...

451
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:19,100
No matter what, get Jade
and save her.

452
00:21:19,233 --> 00:21:20,433
[SANDRO] By the time
the cops arrive,

453
00:21:20,567 --> 00:21:21,867
I would've killed you all then!

454
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:24,400
- And I'll kill her first!
- [GUN COCKS]

455
00:21:25,033 --> 00:21:27,233
- [SCREAMS]
- Kiko!

456
00:21:28,467 --> 00:21:29,700
- Kiko!
- Kiko!

457
00:21:29,833 --> 00:21:31,500
Kiko? Kiko!

458
00:21:31,633 --> 00:21:32,567
Kiko!

459
00:21:32,700 --> 00:21:34,500
- [GROANS IN PAIN]
- Kiko!

460
00:21:34,633 --> 00:21:35,900
Kiko!

461
00:21:36,033 --> 00:21:41,467
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

462
00:21:46,633 --> 00:21:53,467
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

463
00:22:01,033 --> 00:22:08,067
[MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]

464
00:22:10,333 --> 00:22:17,200
[CRYING]

465
00:22:18,333 --> 00:22:20,233
Kiko!

466
00:22:20,367 --> 00:22:23,467
[SOBBING] Kiko!

467
00:22:23,600 --> 00:22:25,267
Kiko...

468
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:30,700
[SOBBING CONTINUES]

469
00:22:30,833 --> 00:22:32,533
Kiko...

470
00:22:32,667 --> 00:22:33,967
Kiko!

471
00:22:34,100 --> 00:22:37,167
[WAILING] Kiko!

472
00:22:37,300 --> 00:22:40,033
Kiko, you promised
not to leave me!

473
00:22:40,167 --> 00:22:41,067
Kiko!

474
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:43,200
Kiko, you need to fight!

475
00:22:43,333 --> 00:22:44,467
Hold on!

476
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:46,700
Don't leave us, Kiko!

477
00:22:46,833 --> 00:22:48,433
[GIO SOBBING]

478
00:22:48,600 --> 00:22:50,100
[MARTIN] Don't leave us!

479
00:22:50,233 --> 00:22:52,300
- Kiko!
- Kiko, wake up!

480
00:22:52,433 --> 00:22:53,700
- Kiko!
- Kiko!

481
00:22:53,833 --> 00:22:55,567
Kiko!

482
00:22:55,700 --> 00:22:57,433
[SOBBING CONTINUES]

483
00:22:57,567 --> 00:22:59,433
Don't leave us, Kiko!

484
00:22:59,567 --> 00:23:01,767
- Kiko, hold on!
- Kiko!

485
00:23:01,900 --> 00:23:03,400
Kiko!

486
00:23:03,533 --> 00:23:04,400
Kiko, please!

487
00:23:04,533 --> 00:23:07,067
Kiko! Kiko!

488
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:08,533
Kiko!

489
00:23:08,667 --> 00:23:09,933
Kiko!

490
00:23:10,833 --> 00:23:12,067
Kiko!

491
00:23:12,967 --> 00:23:14,200
[JADE] Kiko!

492
00:23:14,333 --> 00:23:16,833
Kiko, no!

493
00:23:16,967 --> 00:23:19,900
Kiko, no!

494
00:23:20,600 --> 00:23:23,067
- Kiko!
- [CRYING]

495
00:23:23,933 --> 00:23:25,133
Kiko!

496
00:23:25,267 --> 00:23:32,000
[SOBBING]

497
00:23:32,133 --> 00:23:33,800
[MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]

498
00:23:33,933 --> 00:23:37,300
<i>You know, I'm sure
Monette is proud of you.</i>

499
00:23:37,433 --> 00:23:39,700
<i>As long as Monette's
memories live in my heart,</i>

500
00:23:40,867 --> 00:23:43,433
<i>Hotel 88 will always hold
a special place in me.</i>

501
00:23:44,433 --> 00:23:47,367
<i>Even if we're not destined
together by the universe,</i>

502
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:50,600
<i> I will still choose you.</i>

503
00:23:53,633 --> 00:23:55,100
<i> This is a promise ring.</i>

504
00:23:55,267 --> 00:23:57,700
<i>I promise not
to leave you again.</i>

505
00:23:58,867 --> 00:24:00,967
<i>And we will be together
for life.</i>

506
00:24:02,300 --> 00:24:04,533
<i>Kiko never found
the golden egg.</i>

507
00:24:04,667 --> 00:24:06,000
We'd always tell him

508
00:24:06,133 --> 00:24:08,267
<i>that only the brave ones
find the golden egg.</i>
